data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: 1. Slice Sweet Onion and place into a large pan 2. Take the skin off the Garlic Cloves and place in pan 3. Add the Soy Sauce and the Vinegar 5. (Optional) - Add bay leaf or whatever your mom or grandma adds to their recipe 6. Bring to a boil then simmer for 1 hour 7. Enjoy with your favorite side dish (rice)
